Author: MissNietzsche
Text: I only want to be a couple pounds underweight, so I'm like "Don't worry, I still have BED. My ED is totally not going to flip very soon. /s"  I'm fairly sure most ED people just lower their goal weights once they reach them and are unhappy with them. I reached mine not too long ago that I set when I was like 15 and more BED than restrictive (think it's like a BMI of 20?), and I'm just like "what the hell was I thinking, setting one so high..I'm practically still obese"

Author: 3cats_in_atrenchcoat
Text: Unfortunately for me, wanting to be underweight isn't a requirement of having an ed. I feel you.
